data.text:
Sabor Speaker sure new parl. majority will function well

ZAGREB, May 5 (Hina) - The newly elected president of the Croatian 151-seat parliament, Croatian Democratic Union (HDZ) official Gordan Jandrokovic, said on Friday that the new majority of 76 lawmakers that had supported his election would function well, although that majority consisted of the HDZ plus other 17 parties and independent MPs.
